question:
What is the result of the following C++ code using the Left Shift operator?

```cpp
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int x = 5;
    cout << (x << 1) << endl;
    return 0;
}
```

What will the following code output?

```cpp
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int x = 3;
    cout << (x << 2) << endl;
    return 0;
}
```

